text: In case you see this gura, as far as sleep goes, I had a similar problem of not sleeping until dawn. I managed to fix my schedule by first transitioning it into a biphasic sleep schedule. I first did a 5ish hour cycle from 6ish to 11ish and then another from 3pm to 6pm. Eventually, when I cut out my second cycle, I found myself better able to sleep at more reasonable times (like 2 or 3 am instead of 6 or 7). Don‚Äôt know if this will actually help, but I wanted to throw out my own experience w it.
